FormalTypeParameter.LazyTypeAlias
public class ConstructedType
extends TypeIndirection

This class represents types created as a result of looking up (resolving) a generic parameter, which itself is not a type.

Description copied from class: Type
Check if this type equals the given other type. This is a unidirectional check to keep things extensible. It is fine if equals(other) is false, but other.equals(this) is true.
